body.p: Hickman County, Kentucky, farmer. Kentucky native. Married to Elizabeth A. Kennedy. Father of Milton J. Kennedy, Jo Ella Kennedy, Julia A. Kennedy, Susan M. Kennedy, Sarah F. Kennedy, and Alice Kennedy. Farmer in Moscow, Kentucky, in 1860. Owned eight enslaved persons in 1860.
